(1267, 575, 'criteria', '<b>Please send the following to Submissions@</b><b>GreenGravelComedyFest.com:</b>\r\n\r\nName, City/State, Email, Synopsis (if a one-person show or podcast) Video Link, Website or Credits.\r\n\r\nSubmission Fees should be sent to the same email via PayPal. Submissions that are not accompanied by the submission fee will not be considered.\r\n\r\nAll submissions are due by midnight on Monday, January 5th. No submissions will be accepted after this time and any submission fees from late entrants will be returned.\r\n\r\n*Note: We will be premiering an outreach program for Green Gravel performers to come out to LA to showcase work in front of industry professionals in 2015. Eligibility for this program will be available exclusively to performers who have been previously accepted to perform at Green Gravel functions.\r\n\r\nGG 2015 is already slated to feature some of Iowa''s great indie/alt comedy shows/performers: JANICE, Little Village Comedy Hour, Paperback Rhino and more! We cant wait for you to join them and look forward to seeing your best stuff!\r\n\r\n-The Green Gravel Team'),
